      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've been driving through the mountains for days just looking at everything. the views are beautiful i guess, but i feel like i've seen it all. like i've checked all the boxes on the itinerary and there's nothing left to see. it just feels like i've reached the end of the road and there's nowhere left to go.",
